  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Game

    Instruction is the class that connects InstructionModel and InstructionView.
    Level
    Level is the class that connects LevelSelectionModel, LevelView and LevelController.
    Main
    The main class that enable the game to run.
    Menu
    Start is the class that connects MenuModel, MenuView and MenuController.
    NameSubmit
    NameSubmit is the class that connects NameModel, NameView and NameController.
